ADDITIONAL INFORMATION (FOR EDUCATIONAL & DEMONSTRATION PURPOSE)

1. Project Nature:
This project is developed strictly for educational and demonstration purposes as part of an internship and learning exercise in full-stack development.

2. No Commercial Use Guarantee:
This application is not intended for production-grade commercial usage without further enhancements, security hardening, and compliance implementations.

3. Data & Privacy Notice:
- This application does NOT collect, store, or process any sensitive personal user data.
- No real personal identification details are required to use the system.
- Any user-related data used in the system is minimal and only for demonstration purposes.

4. Payment Disclaimer:
- This project does NOT include any real payment gateway integration.
- No financial transactions are processed within this application.
- Any payment-related UI elements are purely for simulation purposes only.

5. Security Note:
- No confidential credentials (such as database URLs, passwords, or API keys) are exposed in the public version of this project.
- Environment variables are recommended for any sensitive configurations in real deployments.

6. Developer Responsibility:
Users of this software are responsible for implementing proper security, authentication, and data protection mechanisms before using it in real-world applications.

7. Learning Outcome:
This project demonstrates:
- Full-stack architecture (Frontend + Backend)
- REST API integration
- Cloud deployment (Render)
- Database connectivity (MySQL)

